OL,4,CCovid: CO2 monitors pledged to aid
OL,5,Cschool ventilation
OL,6, Around 300,000 carbon dioxide monitors
OL,7, are to be made available to schools in
OL,8, England next term to help improve
OL,9, ventilation and lessen Covid outbreaks.
OL,11,FThe Department for Education said the
OL,12,Fportable monitors could be used to
OL,13,Fidentify areas where more air-flow is
OL,14,Fneeded.
OL,16,FTeaching unions have been calling for
OL,17,Furgent extra ventilation measures.
OL,19,FThey welcomed the pledge, but added any
OL,20,Fventilation needs picked up by the
OL,21,Fmonitors must be acted upon.
